# Server Workflows

- Never run `go mod tidy` directly. Run `make modules-tidy` from `server/` instead; it excludes private enterprise imports that would otherwise break tidy.
- After editing `server/i18n/en.json`, run `make i18n-extract` from `server/`; it regenerates the file with strings in the required order.
